<paragraph id="IFRS10_C1B"><paranum>C1B</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 10"/><data name="paranum" value="C1B"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS10_P0679"><ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Entities</ph></ph> (Amendments to IFRS 10, <xref base="F24730629" href="../ifrs12/IFRS12_TOC.dita#IFRS12_TOC0001" id="IFRS10_X0658">IFRS 12</xref> and <xref base="F24730630" href="../ias27/IAS27_TOC0001.dita#IAS27_TOC0001" id="IFRS10_X0659">IAS 27</xref>), issued in October 2012, amended <xref base="F24730631" href="IFRS10_2.dita#IFRS10_2/IFRS10_2_V2" id="IFRS10_X0660">paragraphs 2</xref>, <xref base="F24730632" href="IFRS10_4.dita#IFRS10_4" id="IFRS10_X0661">4</xref>, <xref base="F24730633" href="IFRS10_C2A.dita#IFRS10_C2A" id="IFRS10_X0662">C2A</xref>, <xref base="F24730634" href="IFRS10_C6A.dita#IFRS10_C6A/IFRS10_C6A_V2" id="IFRS10_X0663">C6A</xref> and <xref base="F26333839" href="IFRS10_APPA.dita#IFRS10_APPA/IFRS10_APPA_TI" id="IFRS10_X0664">Appendix A</xref> and added <xref base="F24730636" id="IFRS10_X0665" keyref="IFRS10_27">paragraphs 27&#x2013;33</xref>, <xref base="F24730637" href="IFRS10_gB85A-B85W_V2.dita" id="IFRS10_X0666" keyref="IFRS10_B85A" scope="local">B85A&#x2013;B85W</xref>, <xref base="F24730638" href="IFRS10_B100.dita#IFRS10_B100" id="IFRS10_X0667">B100&#x2013;B101</xref> and <xref href="IFRS10_C3A.dita" id="IFRS10_X0668" scope="local">C3A&#x2013;C3F</xref>. An entity shall apply those amendments for annual periods beginning on or after 1 January 2014. Early application is permitted. If an entity applies those amendments earlier, it shall disclose that fact and apply all amendments included in <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Entities</ph></ph> at the same time.</p></body></paragraph>